title: Jammu and Kashmir: Two terrorists killed; One AK-47 rifle and pistol recovered by Baramulla Police, 52 Rashtriya Rifles
text:
India news Jammu and Kashmir: Two terrorists killed; One AK-47 rifle and pistol recovered by Baramulla Police, 52 Rashtriya Rifles Jammu and Kashmir: Two terrorists killed; One AK-47 rifle and pistol recovered by Baramulla Police, 52 Rashtriya Rifles The police also recovered 1 AK-47 rifle & 1 pistol from the terrorists. By: FE Online | New Delhi | Published: February 4, 2017 2:07 PM Security forces of India. Source: PTI 
Two terrorists were killed in a joint operation by the Baramulla Police and 52 Rashtriya Rifles (RR), in the Baramulla district of Jammu and Kashmir on Saturday. The police also recovered 1 AK-47 rifle & 1 pistol from the terrorists. The combat operations are underway and the entire area has been segregated off by the security forces. 
Earlier this month, 3 militants were killed in an overnight encounter with security forces in south Kashmirâ€™s Anantnag district. 
(Further details awaited)
